                                            "detail": 0,
                                            "format": 0,
                                            "mode": "normal",
                                            "style": "",
                                            "text": "Xenoplanet is a beautiful open-world adventure game that takes place in a procedurally generated environment. My contributions to Xenonplanet include developing the game’s real time procedural generation systems from the ground up. Designing and implementing combat mechanics and enemy AI that aligned with our desired aesthetics. As well as designing and scripting various mechanics such as the inventory system, world interactions, item drops and more.",
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "version": 1
                                        }
                                    ],
